data.value:
This app is called "Information Gatherer" it is intended to give you your current IP (with or without a VPN) to give you a accurate reading of if you are or not leaking VPN information that can expose your real IP.
* All Data is Terminated when app closes - no .txt files or any files of any kind are created when using this app. * No Data is ever stored. The app is designed to only display to the "Rich Text Box" and not anywhere else on the computer.
